        * ``['a':'z']``, return all keys from *a* to *z* in ascending order.
        * ``['z':'a']``, return all keys from *z* to *a* in reverse order.
        * ``['a':]``, return all key/value pairs from ``a`` on up.
        * ``[:'z']``, return all key/value pairs up to and including ``z``.
